作</span><span leftzone=\"357|4\" rightzone=\"229|4\" space=\"\">的…</span><span leftzone=\"362|15\" rightzone=\"234|15\" space=\"\">描述的</span><span leftzone=\"378|6\" rightzone=\"250|6\" space=\"\">对象，</span><span leftzone=\"385|19\" rightzone=\"257|19\" space=\"\">我必须说，</span><span leftzone=\"405|21\" rightzone=\"277|21\" space=\"\">它看起来像一个巨大的</span><span leftzone=\"427|14\" rightzone=\"299|14\" space=\"\">比萨饼盒</span><span leftzone=\"442|9\" rightzone=\"314|9\" space=\"\">灯</span><span leftzone=\"452|10\" rightzone=\"324|10\" space=\"\">2其</span><span leftzone=\"463|9\" rightzone=\"335|9\" space=\"\">看似</span><span leftzone=\"473|13\" rightzone=\"345|13\" space=\"\">4个侧面板</span><span leftzone=\"487|9\" rightzone=\"359|9\" space=\"\">是</span><span leftzone=\"497|22\" rightzone=\"369|22\" space=\"\">相互对立</span><span leftzone=\"519|1\" rightzone=\"391|1\" space=\"1|\n\">。</span></p> \n <p src=\"When I looked up there was a very large square-possibly triangular, depends if I was seeing it at an angle, machine/craft whatever you want to call it. It seemed to be spinning from right to left and making slow banking maneuvers.... To describe the object I would have to say it looked like a huge pizza box with lights on two of its seemingly 4 side panels that were opposite of each other.\"> <span leftzone=\"519|1\" rightzone=\"391|1\" space=\"1|\n\"><img alt=\"加利福尼亚出现不明飞行物\" src=\"/uploads/allimg/120210/12093S492-0.jpg\"></span></p> \n <div id=\"trans-result-content\"> \n  <p src=\"I was sitting up late last night, or, early however you look at it, watching the NFL Network when I heard the next door neighbor&amp;#39;s two dogs begin to bark franticly. About 2-3 minutes after that I heard a very low soft crescendoing, guttural vibration that was so low it began shaking the cabinets in the kitchen. \"> <span leftzone=\"519|1\" rightzone=\"391|1\" space=\"1|\n\"><span leftzone=\"0|13\" rightzone=\"0|13\" space=\"\">我坐</span><span leftzone=\"14|2\" rightzone=\"14|2\" space=\"\">到</span><span leftzone=\"17|16\" rightzone=\"17|16\" space=\"\">深夜，</span><span leftzone=\"34|2\" rightzone=\"34|2\" space=\"\">或者</span><span leftzone=\"38|5\" rightzone=\"38|5\" space=\"\">早</span><span leftzone=\"36|1\" rightzone=\"36|1\" space=\"\">，</span><span leftzone=\"44|22\" rightzone=\"44|22\" space=\"\">但你看看它</span><span leftzone=\"66|1\" rightzone=\"66|1\" space=\"\">，</span><span leftzone=\"68|12\" rightzone=\"68|12\" space=\"\">看</span><span leftzone=\"81|11\" rightzone=\"81|11\" space=\"\">橄榄球网络</span><span leftzone=\"93|12\" rightzone=\"93|12\" space=\"\">当我听到</span><span leftzone=\"106|13\" rightzone=\"106|13\" space=\"\">隔壁</span><span leftzone=\"120|8\" rightzone=\"120|8\" space=\"\">邻居</span><span leftzone=\"128|6\" rightzone=\"128|6\" space=\"\">的</span><span leftzone=\"135|18\" rightzone=\"135|18\" space=\"\">狗开始叫了</span><span leftzone=\"154|9\" rightzone=\"154|9\" space=\"\">疯狂的</span><span leftzone=\"163|1\" rightzone=\"163|1\" space=\"\">。</span><span leftzone=\"165|9\" rightzone=\"165|9\" space=\"\">约2 - 3</span><span leftzone=\"175|13\" rightzone=\"175|13\" space=\"\">分钟后</span><span leftzone=\"189|4\" rightzone=\"189|4\" space=\"\">，</span><span leftzone=\"194|9\" rightzone=\"194|9\" space=\"\">我听到一个</span><span leftzone=\"204|8\" rightzone=\"204|8\" space=\"\">很低的</span><span leftzone=\"213|4\" rightzone=\"213|4\" space=\"\">软</span><span leftzone=\"218|12\" rightzone=\"218|12\" space=\"\">crescendoing</span><span leftzone=\"230|1\" rightzone=\"230|1\" space=\"\">，</span><span leftzone=\"232|8\" rightzone=\"232|8\" space=\"\">咽喉</span><span leftzone=\"241|14\" rightzone=\"241|14\" space=\"\">振动</span><span leftzone=\"256|13\" rightzone=\"256|13\" space=\"\">很低，</span><span leftzone=\"270|17\" rightzone=\"270|17\" space=\"\">开始动摇了</span><span leftzone=\"288|23\" rightzone=\"288|23\" space=\"\">橱柜在厨房</span><span leftzone=\"311|1\" rightzone=\"311|1\" space=\"1|\n\">。</span></span></p> \n  <p src=\"At first I thought it was our heating unit making crazy noises but I soon realized the sound was coming from outside. I stepped out side my front door and instantly I found the source of the sounds. When I looked up there was a very large square-possibly triangular, depends if I was seeing it at an angle, machine/craft whatever you want to call it. It seemed to be spinning from right to left and making slow banking maneuvers. \"> <span leftzone=\"519|1\" rightzone=\"391|1\" space=\"1|\n\"><span leftzone=\"317|18\" rightzone=\"0|18\" space=\"\">起初我以为</span><span leftzone=\"336|10\" rightzone=\"19|10\" space=\"\">这是我们的</span><span leftzone=\"347|12\" rightzone=\"30|12\" space=\"\">加热单元</span><span leftzone=\"360|12\" rightzone=\"43|12\" space=\"\">做疯狂的</span><span leftzone=\"373|6\" rightzone=\"56|6\" space=\"\">噪音，</span><span leftzone=\"380|19\" rightzone=\"63|19\" space=\"\">但我很快意识到</span><span leftzone=\"400|13\" rightzone=\"83|13\" space=\"\">声音是</span><span leftzone=\"414|19\" rightzone=\"97|19\" space=\"\">从外面走来</span><span leftzone=\"433|1\" rightzone=\"116|1\" space=\"\">。</span><span leftzone=\"435|13\" rightzone=\"118|13\" space=\"\">我走出</span><span leftzone=\"449|7\" rightzone=\"132|7\" space=\"\">我的</span><span leftzone=\"457|14\" rightzone=\"140|14\" space=\"\">前门</span><span leftzone=\"472|11\" rightzone=\"155|11\" space=\"\">我立刻</span><span leftzone=\"484|5\" rightzone=\"167|5\" space=\"\">找到</span><span leftzone=\"490|24\" rightzone=\"173|24\" space=\"\">来源的声音</span><span leftzone=\"514|1\" rightzone=\"197|1\" space=\"\">。</span><span leftzone=\"516|16\" rightzone=\"199|16\" space=\"\">当我抬起头，</span><span leftzone=\"533|22\" rightzone=\"216|22\" space=\"\">有一个非常大</span><span leftzone=\"556|15\" rightzone=\"239|15\" space=\"\">square-possibly</span><span leftzone=\"572|10\" rightzone=\"255|10\" space=\"\">三角形</span><span leftzone=\"582|1\" rightzone=\"265|1\" space=\"\">，</span><span leftzone=\"584|10\" rightzone=\"267|10\" space=\"\">如果</span><span class=\"highlight\" leftzone=\"595|12\" rightzone=\"278|12\" space=\"\">我看到了</span><span leftzone=\"608|14\" rightzone=\"291|14\" space=\"\">它的角度</span><span leftzone=\"622|1\" rightzone=\"305|1\" space=\"\">，</span><span leftzone=\"624|8\" rightzone=\"307|8\" space=\"\">设备/</span><span leftzone=\"632|5\" rightzone=\"315|5\" space=\"\">工艺</span><span leftzone=\"638|28\" rightzone=\"321|28\" space=\"\">你叫它什么</span><span leftzone=\"666|1\" rightzone=\"349|1\" space=\"\">。</span><span leftzone=\"668|15\" rightzone=\"351|15\" space=\"\">它似乎是</span><span leftzone=\"684|13\" rightzone=\"367|13\" space=\"\">从</span><span leftzone=\"698|17\" rightzone=\"381|17\" space=\"\">右至左和</span><span leftzone=\"716|11\" rightzone=\"399|11\" space=\"\">缓慢</span><span leftzone=\"728|17\" rightzone=\"411|17\" space=\"\">倾斜动作</span><span leftzone=\"745|1\" rightzone=\"428|1\" space=\"1|\n\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p> </p>\n </div> \n <div class=\"bdsharebuttonbox\" style=\"margin-left: 590px;\">\n  <a href=\"#\" class=\"bds_more\" data-cmd=\"more\"></a>\n  <a href=\"#\" class=\"bds_qzone\" data-cmd=\"qzone\" title=\"分享到QQ空间\"></a>\n  <a href=\"#\" class=\"bds_tsina\" data-cmd=\"tsina\" title=\"分享到新浪微博\"></a>\n  <a href=\"#\" class=\"bds_tqq\" data-cmd=\"tqq\" title=\"分享到腾讯微博\"></a>\n  <a href=\"#\" class=\"bds_renren\" data-cmd=\"renren\" title=\"分享到人人网\"></a>\n  <a href=\"#\" class=\"bds_weixin\" data-cmd=\"weixin\" title=\"分享到微信\"></a>\n </div> \n</div><center> \n <div class=\"bdlikebutton bdlikebutton-blue bdlikebutton-medium bdlikebutton-medium-blue\">\n  <div class=\"bdlikebutton-inner\">\n   <span class=\"bdlikebutton-add\">+1</span>\n   <div class=\"bdlikebutton-count\">\n    0\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"bdlikebutton-text\">\n    顶\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n</center><div class=\"paging\"> \n <div class=\"pg\"> \n  <a>共2页: </a>\n  <a href=\"#\">上一页</a>\n  <strong class=\"active\">1</strong>\n  <a href=\"1388_2.html\">2</a>\n  <a href=\"1388_2.html\">下一页</a> \n </div> \n</div><div id=\"cyEmoji\" role=\"cylabs\" 